{
  "title": "理解生产者和消费者",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div><a href=\"http://www.infoq.com/cn/articles/producers-and-consumers-mode\">http://www.infoq.com/cn/articles/producers-and-consumers-mode</a><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">生产者消费者模式是通过一个容器来解决生产者和消费者的强耦合问题。生产者和消费者彼此之间不直接通讯，而通过阻塞队列来进行通讯，所以生产者生产完数据之后不用等待消费者处理，直接扔给阻塞队列，消费者不找生产者要数据，而是直接从阻塞队列里取，阻塞队列就相当于一个缓冲区，平衡了生产者和消费者的处理能力。</span><br></div><div><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></span></div><div><br></div><div><br></div><div><br></div>"
    }
  ]
}